  "title": "Sales & Business Development Manager $6K - $7K + Variable Bonus + Own Car (Hazardous and Toxic Waste Management Services)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Full-time, Senior-level role</li><li>Exposure to Offshore, Marine & Industrial clients</li><li>Career growth in Environmental & Hazardous Waste Management Sector</li></ul><p><strong>Role Summary</strong></p><p>You will develop new business opportunities, manage key accounts, and deliver customised solutions aligned with environmental regulations.</p><p><strong>Key Duties</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and execute sales strategies to grow market share</li><li>Identify and meet new clients across industrial, marine & commercial sectors</li><li>Prepare proposals, tenders & service agreements</li><li>Manage key accounts and maintain strong client relationships</li><li>Work closely with operations & technical teams</li><li>Ensure compliance with NEA, IMO & Basel Convention requirements</li><li>Track sales performance and report to Management</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Environmental Science, Business, Engineering, or related field</li><li><strong>Minimum 10 years B2B sales experience</strong> (Toxic Waste / Environmental / Industrial preferred)</li><li>Strong knowledge of hazardous & toxic waste solutions</li><li>Proven sales performance and key account management experience</li><li>Strong communication, negotiation & presentation skills</li><li>CRM, Microsoft Office & proposal writing proficiency</li></ul><p><strong>Apply Now:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:jeffrey@oaktree.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">jeffrey@oaktree.com.sg</a><br /><strong>Contact:</strong> Jeffrey Chua Kay Hwee<br /><strong>EA License No:</strong> 06C4642 | <strong>EA Reg No:</strong> R1110624</p>",
